#: addons/field_army.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"The first player to station an army equivalent in strength to the selected "
"number of fully trained heroes in his tribe’s military sites wins the game. "
"Combination with More Expensive Soldiers add-on recommended."
msgstr ""

#: addons/field_army.wad/init.lua:27 input:27 standard
msgid ""
"The first player to station an army equivalent in strength to the selected "
"number of fully trained heroes in his tribe’s military sites wins the game. "
"THIS STARTING CONDITION IS NOT LIMITED BY TIME! WITH EVERY 5 MINUTES YOU "
"SELECT 1 HERO. One hero has a value of approximately 11 new untrained "
"soldiers (or points)."
